summary: Highlights from the moomin coloured comic “moomin and family life” available here (moomin hunt p3 / Comics / Color comics) So...
caption:
Highlights from the moomin coloured comic “moomin and family life” available here (moomin hunt p3 / Comics / Color comics)

So basically, my reactions :

The third picture perfectly represent my reaction to MOOMINTROLL HAVING BEEN LOST AS A CHILD ? WHY DID NO ONE TALK ABOUT THIS

Then, in order :

+ wE leAd a vErY oRdinAry miDdLe-cLaSs liFe

+ Moominpapa gives no fucks about his son he just met again a week ago and who he hasn’t seen for YEARS and just wants to live in a CAVE with his WIFE (relatable.)

+ if you bro is ever sad, just go for a swim. Also, have you noticed how snufkin lifts his cape before entering the ocean ? Princess. What a princess.

+ There are only two genders : MAN or MOUSE

+ if you bro doesn’t know how to cook and put fucking GUN POWDER IN HIS PANCAKES just tell him to live with you in your tent.

+ you will have a good time.

+ get you a bro who will SWIM and SINK with you. (goals)

+ Moomin and Maiden’s “let us be sensible about this” represent my two last braincells whenever something happens.

+ bi disaster snufkin.

+ Snufkin will never know if he met other criminal pals.

summary: Moomins Reverse AU where Moomin is a solitary traveller who wanders the world during the colder months getting in touch with his...
body:
Moomins Reverse AU where Moomin is a solitary traveller who wanders the world during the colder months getting in touch with his Moomin Hunter Side, oh boy only to return in the spring to Mumrikvalley, where his not-quite-human boyfriend Snufkin stays and hibernates like a cat in front of the fireplace all winter while his parents find … other ways of keeping warm upstairs.

Bonus:

The Mymbles move around a lot because of their 👀 pastimes, making larger and larger houses in different areas of the valley to house each new onslaught of kids - you can find dozens of their old houses, no longer lived in, littered about the valley, some of which have been cheekily taken over by other residents to live in instead.

Because of this, on the first day of spring, Snufkin will wake up on cue and amble outside to play his harmonica to let Moomin know where his new home is and help guide him over 😳

caption:
[ID start: a page of 4 black and white doodles of Snufkin. Snufkin is a man with a light skin tone, short hair, and a tail like a lion. He is wearing a big pointed hat with a flower crown around it or a feather stuck on it, as well as a large baggy shirt, pants, and boots with straps, The first drawing is him standing and smoking his pipe, The second is him closing his eyes as he sits with his legs crossed, playing the harmonica. The third is him holding onto the straps of his backpack as he smiles. The fourth is him sitting on a bench as he raises his hands up. end ID]
